", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 12, "score_up": 180, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASFqpq85C", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 153, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8434362, "raw_content": "The President can impose tariffs via other laws, such as:\n\n- Section 232 (Trade Expansion Act 1962) for national security threats.\n- Section 301 (Trade Act 1974) for unfair trade practices.\n- Section 201 (Trade Act 1974) against import surges.\n- Section 122 (Trade Act 1974) for balance-of-payments issues.\n\nThe SCOTUS ruling only restricts IEEPA.\n\nDon't get upset by all the master rage baiters.\n", "author": "Herpawinski", "created": 1771603893848, "profile_picture": "GCJCeufYDd47", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "blockchain-the-vote", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Calm down. The Scotus ruling only applies their implementation via IEEPA. There are multiple other avenues to enact tariffs.", "last_comment_created": 1771608809860, "content": "<p>The President can impose tariffs via other laws, such as:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Section 232 (Trade Expansion Act 1962) for national security threats.</li>\n<li>Section 301 (Trade Act 1974) for unfair trade practices.</li>\n<li>Section 201 (Trade Act 1974) against import surges.</li>\n<li>Section 122 (Trade Act 1974) for balance-of-payments issues.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The SCOTUS ruling only restricts IEEPA.</p>\n<p>Don't get upset by all the master rage baiters.</p>\n", "score_down": 2, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 155, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASFqojO3d", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 301, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8433999, "raw_content": "", "author": "ArthurJ", "created": 1771590438783, "profile_picture": "2n7j40CvvfEB", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "mailinvoter", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASFqojO3d.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/YAop8LMdEfU3.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/woffoDHZxoTtSUas.jpeg", "width": 626, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "UII4@QD+OAt6,]s:OXbH_4%09uWX01s.XRR+", "full_resolution": [870, 709]}, "title": "Next Netflix Blockbuster .....", "last_comment_created": 1771617062207, "content": "", "score_down": 1, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 2, "score_up": 302, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASFqpqgNi", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 114, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "maga", "id": 8434596, "raw_content": "", "autho